id: https://w3id.org/linkml/examples/rdmoinfo
name: rdmoinfo
prefixes:
  linkml: https://w3id.org/linkml/
  rdmoinfo: https://w3id.org/linkml/examples/rdmoinfo
imports:
  - linkml:types
default_range: string
default_prefix: rdmoinfo

classes:
  RDMO:
    attributes:
      what_is_the_main_research_question_of_the_project:
      please_give_some_keywords_describing_the_research_question:
      to_which_discipline__disciplines_is_the_project_assigned:
      when_does_the_project_start:
      when_does_the_project_end:
      which_persons_or_institutions_are_responsible_for_the_project_coordination:
      are_there_other_data_management_requirements_eg_from_the_scientific_community_that_need_to_be_considered:
      what_kind_of_data_set_is_it:
      is_the_data_set_generated_or_reused:
      if_reused_who_created_the_data_set:
      if_reused_at_what_address_pid_or_url_is_the_data_set_available:
      is_the_data_set_reproducible_ie_could_it_be_recreated_or_recovered_if_it_were_lost:
      what_is_the_size_of_the_data_set:
      what_file_formats_are_used:
      are_different_versions_of_the_data_set_created:
      what_technology_or_tool_is_used_for_versioning:
      what_will_this_data_set_be_used_forhow_will_it_be_used_during_the_project:
      how_often_will_this_data_set_be_used:
      to_what_extent_will_infrastructure_resources_be_required_eg_cpu_hours_bandwidth_storage_space_etc:
      are_there_actual_or_potential_usage_scenarios_that_could_benefit_from_support_by_a_data_management_or_it_expert_or_that_even_require_such_support:
      where_is_the_data_set_stored_during_the_project:
      are_there_internal_project_guidelines_for_consistent_data_organisation:
      is_there_an_internal_project_guideline_for_naming_the_data:
      is_this_data_set_interoperable_ie_can_it_be_shared_and_reused_between_researchers_institutions_organisations_countries_etc:
      will_this_data_set_be_published_or_shared:
      if_so_where_are_the_data_published:
      if_so_under_which_terms_of_use_or_license_is_the_data_set_published_or_shared:
      will_the_data_be_collaboratively_used:
      which_platform__tools_is__are_used_for_collaboratively_working_on_data_and_publications:
      how_is_the_collaborative_work_on_the_same_files_organised:
      what_quality_assurance_measures_are_in_place_for_this_data_set:
      what_metadata_is_collected_automatically:
      are_metadata_and_contextual_information_checked_for_correctness_and_completeness:
      who_is_responsible_for_documenting_and_checking_the_metadata_and_contextual_information_for_accuracy_and_completeness:
      please_briefly_explain_the_structure_and_the_relationship_between_your_data:
      are_persistent_identifiers_pids_used_for_this_data_set:
      what_system_of_persistent_identifiers_is_used:
      does_the_legal_situation_of_different_countries_have_to_be_considered:
      does_this_data_set_contain_personal_data:
      does_this_data_set_contain_nonpersonal_sensitive_data:
      has_the_research_project_been_reviewed_by_an_ethics_committee:
      is_a_legal_approval__permit_needed_for_the_research:
      is_a_data_access_committee_required_to_decide_whether_or_not_to_grant_access_to_data_published_by_the_project_in_response_to_access_requests:
      is_data_used_andor_created_that_is_protected_by_copyright_or_related_rights:
      does_this_data_set_have_to_be_preserved_for_the_longterm:
      what_are_the_reasons_for_this_data_set_to_be_preserved_for_the_longterm:
      how_long_must_the_data_be_stored:
      how_long_should_the_data_be_reusable_after_the_end_of_the_project:
      where_will_the_data_including_metadata_documentation_and_any_relevant_code_or_software_be_stored_or_archived_after_the_project_is_completed:
      is_the_repository_or_data_centre_chosen_certified_eg_data_seal_of_approval_nestor_seal_or_iso_16363:
      have_appropriate_archiving_solutions_already_been_discussed_with_the_repository_or_data_centre:
      how_is_the_identity_of_persons_accessing_the_data_verified:
      who_is_the_longterm_contact_person_who_can_make_decisions_about_the_data:
      please_enter_the_email_address_of_the_permanent_contact_named_above:
